{"tid":2358844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河北爆疫 港府拒收緊入境","createTime":"2021-01-08T12:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T10:58:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ac8589d914fd350aefafb0bdf95a20efb23afa","tid":2358844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/Z6EAZQO4TJABNOZT44UHGYXBWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FZ6EAZQO4TJABNOZT44UHGYXBWM%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f935176a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FZ6EAZQO4TJABNOZT44UHGYXBWM%2F&h=d02fb72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/Z6EAZQO4TJABNOZT44UHGYXBWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n河北爆疫 港府拒收緊入境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/REENIPHgq5V1nvhb4_ezuW9xkuc=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZV3MGANXFC7BIUYZ6AWLREYUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FREENIPHgq5V1nvhb4_ezuW9xkuc%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZV3MGANXFC7BIUYZ6AWLREYUE.jpg&h=a900eef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地疫情反覆，港府仍未收緊入境管制；圖為深圳灣口岸。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府對英國封關，令滯留當地的港人不能回港，對內地卻採取雙重標準。食物及衞生局副局長徐德義昨被問及河北省疫情大爆發時表示，在河北的港人可以繼續回港，只需在關口領取樣本樽後即可入境。<br />\n<br />\n據中國國家衞建委公佈。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅關口派樣本瓶<br />\n<br />\n徐德義昨被問及河北省出現疫情爆發，本港會否收緊入境管制及檢討回港易計劃時，回應指衞生防護中心會密切留意香港以外任何地方的疫情，對於河北省確診個案上升，政府已宣佈1月6日起，香港居民在過去14天到過河北省，入境時均會在關口獲發樣本瓶，並需依照指示自行收集及交回深喉唾液樣本，以進行病毒檢測。當局會密切留意各地疫情，有需要時調整入境管制措施。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府對河北的寬鬆態度，與英國截然不同，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1141d0f2176bfbf9451118021cc01cc61620a11a","tid":2358844,"uid":340081,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"傷害兩地人民感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e56349f8767e2a8d1b98e438a9aeeb3736c6f70","tid":2358844,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328bfced91e695ada071bca42acc36f58dde510b","tid":2358844,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"第五波安心出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1ba1febd07c9d42732c358f7a4223465af29c7","tid":2358844,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"328bfced91e695ada071bca42acc36f58dde510b","tid":2358844,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"第五波安心出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78ed677f7673825880f6f751ac85d5f0545b92a","tid":2358844,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"人哋澳洲 各省可以互封 香港竟然 唔敢封<br />\n<br />\n人口密集到咁 有事起上嚟 香港大獲過中國好多<br />\n<br />\nd狗官會唔知？ <br />\n<br />\n唔知又搞乜陰謀 迫害香港人 同搶＄"},{"pid":"c90f938b0879038c82218fb21922cb2188e1ca4f","tid":2358844,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"距離第五波不遠了"},{"pid":"feded1ebd1383948fe530ddc44eedff331503a04","tid":2358844,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d78ed677f7673825880f6f751ac85d5f0545b92a","tid":2358844,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"人哋澳洲 各省可以互封 香港竟然 唔敢封<br />\n<br />\n人口密集到咁 有事起上嚟 香港大獲過中國好多<br />\n<br />\nd狗官會唔知？ <br />\n<br />\n唔知又搞乜陰謀 迫害香港人 同搶＄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"佢就係想"},{"pid":"051322ad484a656d727def47b007e6b20821d66d","tid":2358844,"uid":375068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"快啲走啦"}]}